Package: AMRapp
Title: Antimicrobial Resistance Trend Analysis Visualisations
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Rebecca", "Guy", , "rebecca.guy@cranfield.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5500-5691"))
Description: AMRapp provides functionality to build interactive antimicrobial resistance (AMR) data summaries and visualisations. Also provided is a Shiny option to upload, filter and select visulaisation options. Export facilities are inbuilt.
